content.html: This is an odd question for Google to ask me! Don’t they know the answer even better than I do? Maybe it’s a social experiment to compare people’s perceptions of their search frequency with the reality? Or maybe a test to see whether people are honest about their search habit?
content.value:
This is an odd question for Google to ask me! Don’t they know the answer even better than I do?

Maybe it’s a social experiment to compare people’s perceptions of their search frequency with the reality? Or maybe a test to see whether people are honest about their search habit?
